OL,3,CRadio stations to stop broadcasting
OL,4,Cfrom iconic tower
OL,6,FLiverpool's iconic Radio City Tower,
OL,7,Fthe St Johns Beacon, will no longer be
OL,8,Fthe home of the city's radio station.
OL,10,FBauer Media, who own the Hits Radio
OL,11,FLiverpool and Greatest Hits Radio
OL,12,FBreakfast shows that broadcast from
OL,13,Fthe tower, are not renewing the lease
OL,14,Fon the iconic building.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Bauer Media Audio
OL,17,FUK said: "We are incredibly proud to
OL,18,Fhave been part of the vibrant history
OL,19,Fof the Grade II listed St Johns Beacon.
