OL,6,F"This next step allows us to invest in
OL,7,Ffacilities that better support our
OL,8,Fvision and evolving needs. The final
OL,9,Fshows from St Johns Beacon will air
OL,10,Fbefore Christmas 2024.
OL,12,F"Following this date, Greatest Hits
OL,13,FRadio Breakfast will broadcast
OL,14,Fnationally from Bauer's Northwest hub,
OL,15,Fwhilst Hits Radio Liverpool Breakfast
OL,16,Fwill continue to broadcast from the
OL,17,Fcity."
OL,19,FRadio City was founded in 1974 and St
OL,20,FJohns Beacon has housed Bauer stations
OL,21,Fsince 2000.
