OL,6,FSome of Radio City's famous names have
OL,7,Fbeen reacting to the news, Pete Price
OL,8,Fsaid on X: "What a very sad
OL,9,Fannouncement that Bauer Media are
OL,10,Fleaving St John's Beacon.
OL,12,F"I've had the most amazing career with
OL,13,Fa lot of my time spent in that iconic
OL,14,Ftower, it really is a sad day.
OL,16,FThe last programmes will be made at
OL,17,Fthe tower on Christmas Eve. The
OL,18,Fcompany plan to keep leasing the
OL,19,Ffamous sign but want to change the
OL,20,Fwording.
